{"title":"思之歌","authors":["王承典"],"dates":[{"year":1989,"month":3,"day":22}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"思之歌"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"王承典"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有的人操练了半个世纪"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只为等待一个表白的瞬间"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有的人一生都在演戏"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"却来不及吃透一句台词"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"即使割掉舌头"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也不做地狱的歌手"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"即使终生残废"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也要斩断流脓的骨头"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"与其昧着良心跳舞"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"何如放开嗓子诅咒"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在黑色的花朵上市以前"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红花总能卖个好价钱"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"能恪守什么"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"能怀疑什么"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"能憎恨什么"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"能宽容什么"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"每一方天地里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都生活着一批"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"论据充足的真理持有者"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"云多了显得凌乱"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"云没了显得平淡"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只佩戴几朵胸花的蓝天"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有福了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"糖里加点儿盐"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"方能达到甜的最高水准"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"分娩出甜瓜的瓜蒂儿"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"苦得叫人难受"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"由于灭绝生灵的原子弹的诞生"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这世界才显得相对和平"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"蛐蛐们使劲地吵闹"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"秋夜愈是宁静"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有了残梗败叶的映衬"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"夏日荷花才美得出众"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"多情的血渗进无情的铁"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"便具有了惊人的腥红"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}